import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  ChakraProvider,
  Box,
  Flex,
  Tabs,
  TabList,
  TabPanels,
  Tab,
  TabPanel,
  Container,
  Heading,
  Text,
  useColorModeValue,
  Image,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import {
  FaMapMarkedAlt,
  FaRoute,
  FaChartLine,
  FaHotel,
  FaInfoCircle,
} from "react-icons/fa";

// Import components
import Map from "./components/Map";
import Recommendations from "./components/Recommendations";
import Predictions from "./components/Predictions";

function App() {
  // State
  const [currentRoute, setCurrentRoute] = useState(null);
  const [sourceLocation, setSourceLocation] = useState(null);
  const [destinationLocation, setDestinationLocation] = useState(null);
  const [prediction, setPrediction] = useState(null);

  // Handle route calculation
  const handleRouteCalculated = (source, destination, route) => {
    setSourceLocation(source);
    setDestinationLocation(destination);
    setCurrentRoute(route);
  };

  // Handle prediction complete
  const handlePredictionComplete = (pred) => {
    setPrediction(pred);
  };

  // Colors
  const bgColor = useColorModeValue("gray.50", "gray.900");
  const headerBg = useColorModeValue("teal.500", "teal.200");
  const headerText = useColorModeValue("white", "gray.800");

  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <Box minH="100vh" bg={bgColor}>
        {/* App Header */}
        <Flex
          as="header"
          align="center"
          justify="space-between"
          wrap="wrap"
          padding={4}
          bg={headerBg}
          color={headerText}
        >
          <Flex align="center" mr={5}>
            <FaRoute size={30} />
            <Heading as="h1" size="lg" ml={2}>
              Traveler Guide System
            </Heading>
          </Flex>

          <Text>
            Optimal routes, predictions, and recommendations for travelers
          </Text>
        </Flex>

        {/* Main Content */}
        <Tabs isFitted variant="enclosed" colorScheme="teal" mt={4}>
          <TabList mb="1em">
            <Tab>
              <Box as={FaMapMarkedAlt} mr={2} /> Map
            </Tab>
            <Tab>
              <Box as={FaChartLine} mr={2} /> Predictions
            </Tab>
            <Tab>
              <Box as={FaHotel} mr={2} /> Recommendations
            </Tab>
            <Tab>
              <Box as={FaInfoCircle} mr={2} /> About
            </Tab>
          </TabList>

          <TabPanels>
            {/* Map Tab */}
            <TabPanel p={0}>
              <Map onRouteCalculated={handleRouteCalculated} />
            </TabPanel>

            {/* Predictions Tab */}
            <TabPanel>
              <Container maxW="container.xl">
                <Predictions
                  source={sourceLocation}
                  destination={destinationLocation}
                  onPredictionComplete={handlePredictionComplete}
                />
              </Container>
            </TabPanel>

            {/* Recommendations Tab */}
            <TabPanel>
              <Container maxW="container.xl">
                <Recommendations
                  userLocation={sourceLocation}
                  route={currentRoute}
                />
              </Container>
            </TabPanel>

            {/* About Tab */}
            <TabPanel>
              <Container maxW="container.xl">
                <Box
                  p={5}
                  shadow="md"
                  borderWidth="1px"
                  borderRadius="lg"
                  bg="white"
                >
                  <Heading as="h2" size="xl" mb={4}>
                    About the Traveler Guide System
                  </Heading>

                  <Text fontSize="lg" mb={4}>
                    Traveler Guide is a comprehensive application designed to
                    help travelers plan their journeys with intelligent routing,
                    accurate travel time predictions, and personalized
                    recommendations.
                  </Text>

                  <Heading as="h3" size="md" mb={3} mt={6}>
                    Key Features
                  </Heading>

                  <Box pl={4} mb={6}>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • Interactive Google Maps with route visualization
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • Optimal route calculation using Dijkstra's and A*
                      algorithms
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • ML-based travel time and traffic predictions
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • Place recommendations (hotels, restaurants, gas
                      stations) using K-Means clustering
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • Route preferences (no tolls, shortest, safest, scenic)
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>• Offline route saving capabilities</Text>
                  </Box>

                  <Heading as="h3" size="md" mb={3}>
                    Technology Stack
                  </Heading>

                  <Box pl={4} mb={6}>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • Frontend: React.js with Google Maps JavaScript API,
                      Chakra UI
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>• Backend: Node.js with Express</Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>
                      • ML Models: Python with scikit-learn and TensorFlow
                    </Text>
                    <Text mb={2}>• Database: MongoDB</Text>
                  </Box>

                  <Text fontSize="sm" color="gray.600" mt={8}>
                    Developed as a demonstration of full-stack development and
                    machine learning integration.
                  </Text>
                </Box>
              </Container>
            </TabPanel>
          </TabPanels>
        </Tabs>
      </Box>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
}

export default App;
